# GitHub Pages Image Hosting Setup

1. Upload the contents of this package to your repo.
2. In GitHub, go to Settings > Pages.
3. Under Build and deployment, choose:
   Source: Deploy from a branch
   Branch: main
   Folder: /root
4. Save and wait 1-3 minutes.
5. Open these in an incognito window:
   https://whoknowz13.github.io/A-New-Executive-Brand-Kit/signature/assets/austin-headshot.jpg
   https://whoknowz13.github.io/A-New-Executive-Brand-Kit/signature/assets/a-new-signature.png
6. If both load, use signature/AustinNewSignature-GitHubPagesImages.html in Modern Retail CRM.
